OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying
OL,6,Fmostly clear and dry this evening,
OL,7,Fwith some patchy cloud moving into the
OL,8,Fwest later. Mist and fog developing in
OL,9,Fsheltered rural locations further east
OL,10,Fwith murky conditions and low cloud
OL,11,Fpossible over western regions. Staying
OL,12,Fmild overnight.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FA mild start to Thursday,
OL,15,Fwith cloud and rain moving into the
OL,16,Fwest through the morning. This clears
OL,17,Feastwards into the afternoon, turning
OL,18,Fcooler behind with blustery showers
OL,19,Fthereafter.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
