OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDrier at
OL,6,Ffirst on Friday with a band of cloud
OL,7,Fand rain arriving from the west later.
OL,8,FRemaining unsettled thereafter with
OL,9,Fsunny spells and scattered showers.
OL,10,FTemperatures nearer to average.
